unofficial McKague calendar (larger size)

This version of the 2000 McKague calendar has a resolution of 100 dpi and a page size of approximately 8.5" x 11". We have no problem printing this size on our printers and it gives a clearer picture than the smaller version. Some relatives have found this too large for their printers so we suggest you experiment and decide what is best for you. We have had better results from downloading the file to the hard drive and printing from there than from printing directly from the net. As web novices, we don't understand all this but maybe you do. Good luck.
